== "Enjoy the services of"

You enjoy the services of someone who is your servant.

If the person would not say, "At your service," you can't say you enjoy their services.

You don't enjoy the services of a doctor, unless he works for you.

The White House enjoys the service of a personal physician. He has an office at 
the White House and whenever someone is sick they can go to see him. The White 
House pays him a salary every month.

