== Second chance

+ If the question is ungrammatical, or there is
some other problem with the question, the player
gets a second chance. If the second attempt is
also ungrammatical, it is a double fault, and the
other player gets a Double Fault point (1).

----
== Answering question

+ If the question is a good question and the other
player answers the question correctly, that player
gets a Returned point (1). If he/she doesn't, the
questioner gets an Unreturned point (1).

----
== How many questions

+ I want you to do at least 4 questions each, one
for each topic.

---
== Scoring questions

+ F = Double Fault (1 for your opponent),
U = Unreturned (1 for you),
R = Returned (1 for your opponent)
O = Old question (Someone else's question)
(you must ask a different question)

